"{\n \"heroTexts\": [\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h1\",\n   \"cls\": \"h1 l:w-auto w-max\",\n   \"text\": \"we create feelings.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h2\",\n   \"cls\": \"h2 section-title text-right\",\n   \"text\": \"Great design doesn’t just guide behavior.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h2\",\n   \"cls\": \"h2 section-title\",\n   \"text\": \"It speaks directly to the nervous system.\"\n  }\n ],\n \"section1\": [\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h2\",\n   \"cls\": \"h1 section-title\",\n   \"text\": \"we activate nerves.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h3\",\n   \"cls\": \"_35 sm_27 font-medium\",\n   \"text\": \"There’s a better way.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14\",\n   \"text\": \"With a collective 30 years in the industry, we've seen it all.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14\",\n   \"text\": \"We believe that marrying best in class creative and production delivers better work, more smoothly, with more impact for your dollar.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14\",\n   \"text\": \"Clarity through communication, understanding through collaboration — it’s what to expect when working with Mantis.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h3\",\n   \"cls\": \"_35 sm_27 font-medium w-[10ch] s:w-full\",\n   \"text\": \"Small Teams, Big Ideas.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14\",\n   \"text\": \"Our global network includes top-tier talent around the world — from creative directors and technologists to writers and producers. We build high-impact teams tailored to your project. No bloat. No busywork. Just the right people doing their best work.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14\",\n   \"text\": \"We encourage those around us to challenge our ways of thinking, push us forward, and in turn — your work thrives.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h3\",\n   \"cls\": \"_35 sm_27 font-medium w-[13ch] s:w-full\",\n   \"text\": \"Streamlined by AI.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14\",\n   \"text\": \"Mantis leverages emerging technologies to connect with your audience in new and exciting ways. As generative AI models rapidly improve, they’re streamlining our processes and helping us work faster and smarter.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14\",\n   \"text\": \"By blending it with the traditional mediums we excel at, we believe the opportunities are endless. It’s a partner in how we work and a tool to make experiences more immersive.\"\n  }\n ],\n \"section2\": [\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h2\",\n   \"cls\": \"h1 section-title\",\n   \"text\": \"we stimulate memory.\"\n  }\n ],\n \"section3\": [\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h2\",\n   \"cls\": \"h1 section-title\",\n   \"text\": \"we excite neurons.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Architecture We build to inspire, but also build to code. At Mantis, design is only as strong as its function. Our architects specialize in bridging imagination with reality, ensuring bold concepts meet practical standards. Our network of fabricators span globally and across specialities; whether you’re creating small scale builds, large permanent structures, or sculpted art pieces - we’ve got you\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Architecture\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"We build to inspire, but also build to code. At Mantis, design is only as strong as its function. Our architects specialize in bridging imagination with reality, ensuring bold concepts meet practical standards. Our network of fabricators span globally and across specialities; whether you’re creating small scale builds, large permanent structures, or sculpted art pieces - we’ve got you covered. REL\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"We build to inspire, but also build to code. At Mantis, design is only as strong as its function. Our architects specialize in bridging imagination with reality, ensuring bold concepts meet practical standards. Our network of fabricators span globally and across specialities; whether you’re creating small scale builds, large permanent structures, or sculpted art pieces - we’ve got you covered.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Spatial & Interior Design A well-designed space balances openness and intimacy to draw people in and keep them engaged. We design with flow, psychology, and resonance in mind, creating environments that invite exploration and spark conversation long after the visit. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionMoodboardsRetailWayfinding and Signage SystemsAR/VR/XR Integration in Physical SpacesEn\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Spatial & Interior Design\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"A well-designed space balances openness and intimacy to draw people in and keep them engaged. We design with flow, psychology, and resonance in mind, creating environments that invite exploration and spark conversation long after the visit. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionMoodboardsRetailWayfinding and Signage SystemsAR/VR/XR Integration in Physical SpacesEnvironmental DesignSpatial \"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"A well-designed space balances openness and intimacy to draw people in and keep them engaged. We design with flow, psychology, and resonance in mind, creating environments that invite exploration and spark conversation long after the visit.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Interactive / Creative Technology Experiences that anticipate what users want and need, paired with intuitive interfaces that support those actions, are our bread and butter. Our network of technologists—equal parts developer and artist—ensures every layer feels purposeful and magical. From reactive environments to projection-mapped performances, we design technology that transforms ideas into “wo\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Interactive / Creative Technology\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"Experiences that anticipate what users want and need, paired with intuitive interfaces that support those actions, are our bread and butter. Our network of technologists—equal parts developer and artist—ensures every layer feels purposeful and magical. From reactive environments to projection-mapped performances, we design technology that transforms ideas into “wow” moments. RELATED SERVICES Creat\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"Experiences that anticipate what users want and need, paired with intuitive interfaces that support those actions, are our bread and butter. Our network of technologists—equal parts developer and artist—ensures every layer feels purposeful and magical. From reactive environments to projection-mapped performances, we design technology that transforms ideas into “wow” moments.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Event Production We always deliver a smooth on-site experience by clearly defining roles & responsibilities, communication plans, escalation paths, detailed run of shows, and call sheets. Ahead of being on-site, we run through a detailed production book – culminating all the project details to use as the source of truth for all teams. RELATED SERVICES Fabrication ManagementStaffing ManagementLogis\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Event Production\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"We always deliver a smooth on-site experience by clearly defining roles & responsibilities, communication plans, escalation paths, detailed run of shows, and call sheets. Ahead of being on-site, we run through a detailed production book – culminating all the project details to use as the source of truth for all teams. RELATED SERVICES Fabrication ManagementStaffing ManagementLogistics / Tour Manag\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"We always deliver a smooth on-site experience by clearly defining roles & responsibilities, communication plans, escalation paths, detailed run of shows, and call sheets. Ahead of being on-site, we run through a detailed production book – culminating all the project details to use as the source of truth for all teams.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"3D Modelling We deliver full-service 3D pipelines tailored to your project. From avatar systems to real-time content for live shows, we build assets designed to impress. Every piece is optimized across platforms so visuals don’t just look great, they perform flawlessly. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionCharacter DesignEnvironment DesignModellingRiggingTexturingOptimization3D Fashion R\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"3D Modelling\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"We deliver full-service 3D pipelines tailored to your project. From avatar systems to real-time content for live shows, we build assets designed to impress. Every piece is optimized across platforms so visuals don’t just look great, they perform flawlessly. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionCharacter DesignEnvironment DesignModellingRiggingTexturingOptimization3D Fashion Reach out for \"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"We deliver full-service 3D pipelines tailored to your project. From avatar systems to real-time content for live shows, we build assets designed to impress. Every piece is optimized across platforms so visuals don’t just look great, they perform flawlessly.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Motion & Animation Strong storytelling drives our work. We collaborate with world-class motion artists who understand movement as one of the most powerful communication tools. Whether constructing entire worlds or animating static designs, motion and animation are central to Mantis. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionStoryboardingAnimaticsMotion GuidelinesInteractive WalkthroughsContent\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Motion & Animation\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"Strong storytelling drives our work. We collaborate with world-class motion artists who understand movement as one of the most powerful communication tools. Whether constructing entire worlds or animating static designs, motion and animation are central to Mantis. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionStoryboardingAnimaticsMotion GuidelinesInteractive WalkthroughsContent AnimationWeb Anima\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"Strong storytelling drives our work. We collaborate with world-class motion artists who understand movement as one of the most powerful communication tools. Whether constructing entire worlds or animating static designs, motion and animation are central to Mantis.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"User Experience / Interface We don’t rely on best practices. Each project begins from scratch to create systems that are genuinely bespoke. When we reference the past, we evolve it into something uniquely yours. Experience is at the core of our approach. Systems of any scale need architects who anticipate behavior before it happens. For over twenty years, we’ve been shaping pioneering interfaces f\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"User Experience / Interface\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"We don’t rely on best practices. Each project begins from scratch to create systems that are genuinely bespoke. When we reference the past, we evolve it into something uniquely yours. Experience is at the core of our approach. Systems of any scale need architects who anticipate behavior before it happens. For over twenty years, we’ve been shaping pioneering interfaces for the web, and we continue \"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"We don’t rely on best practices. Each project begins from scratch to create systems that are genuinely bespoke. When we reference the past, we evolve it into something uniquely yours. Experience is at the core of our approach. Systems of any scale need architects who anticipate behavior before it happens. For over twenty years, we’ve been shaping pioneering interfaces for the web, and we continue \"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Development A digital experience is only as good as it functions. We work with the best technologists early and often in our process to plan and build performant tested experiences. Development makes our work better, and is a critical collaborator in our process at Mantis. RELATED SERVICES Technical DirectionFront-End DevelopmentWebGLCMS IntegrationE-Commerce IntegrationQADeploymentSystems Integra\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Development\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"A digital experience is only as good as it functions. We work with the best technologists early and often in our process to plan and build performant tested experiences. Development makes our work better, and is a critical collaborator in our process at Mantis. RELATED SERVICES Technical DirectionFront-End DevelopmentWebGLCMS IntegrationE-Commerce IntegrationQADeploymentSystems IntegrationPerforma\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"A digital experience is only as good as it functions. We work with the best technologists early and often in our process to plan and build performant tested experiences. Development makes our work better, and is a critical collaborator in our process at Mantis.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Brand & Campaign Strategy Great ideas need direction. We offer scalable strategies—sometimes instinct-driven, sometimes data-backed—that gives your project a clear foundation. We design campaigns around the moments that matter, turning strategy into executions that catch the eye and spark engagement. Campaigns can focus on a single channel or expand into 360º ecosystems—experiential, digital, and \"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Brand & Campaign Strategy\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"Great ideas need direction. We offer scalable strategies—sometimes instinct-driven, sometimes data-backed—that gives your project a clear foundation. We design campaigns around the moments that matter, turning strategy into executions that catch the eye and spark engagement. Campaigns can focus on a single channel or expand into 360º ecosystems—experiential, digital, and content working together. \"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"p\",\n   \"cls\": \"_20 sm_14 leading-1 s:max-w-260\",\n   \"text\": \"Great ideas need direction. We offer scalable strategies—sometimes instinct-driven, sometimes data-backed—that gives your project a clear foundation. We design campaigns around the moments that matter, turning strategy into executions that catch the eye and spark engagement. Campaigns can focus on a single channel or expand into 360º ecosystems—experiential, digital, and content working together.\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-bl\",\n   \"text\": \"Identity Your look, your legacy. As the first handshake with the world, brand identity defines both perception and memory. We build everything from streamlined starter packages to expansive brand universes: logos, tone of voice, creative direction, and more. RELATED SERVICES Graphic DesignVisual SystemsBrand Guidelines Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-row items-center gap-10 px-20 py-20 accordion_top \",\n   \"text\": \"Identity\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"div\",\n   \"cls\": \"accordion_content\",\n   \"text\": \"Your look, your legacy. As the first handshake with the world, brand identity defines both perception and memory. We build everything from streamlined starter packages to exp